{"tid":535983,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X LTE <> 4G","createTime":"2018-01-21T12:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T18:46:05.000Z","uid":155296,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de86a57b855ba141ef1781ba691f0447ab403da4","tid":535983,"uid":155296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:07:32.000Z","msg":"一路都用開CSL, 而我老婆用HKBN<br />\n<br />\n話說我同我老婆一齊換左ipX, 之後發現一樣野<br />\n<br />\n我老婆hkbn 顯示LTE<br />\n已我CSL 係顯示4G<br />\n<br />\n其實有無分別?"},{"pid":"eae0f7995a038a90c647e5af7021e41fc0bbc398","tid":535983,"uid":21488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"d53d7251b4004fa712900166bcb3cf4a4ee44d19","tid":535983,"uid":5846,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:11:12.000Z","msg":"4g 快啲<br />\n<br />\n利申 行內人"},{"pid":"579e5fc6cb9fc2cefab4bfed48d8acc880c58278","tid":535983,"uid":340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"4f182116e8a59efd937af1bef9651b92aff17e35","tid":535983,"uid":22390,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"LTE 係3.9g  CMHK<br />\n4G真係4G   CSL <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4G理論上快過3.9g"},{"pid":"498cd87d0ef59c1ecfdc06ced3d1cbccb013ddf4","tid":535983,"uid":155296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"明白晒, 唔該晒各位巴打"},{"pid":"81592327cd1026df6dba9318314e874b013f7c89","tid":535983,"uid":3223,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"真實上 4G 快過 LTE<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但iPhone 顯示上，就冇，個台想show 咩就咩<br />\n<br />\n入邊只係 &lt;ShowLTEas4G&gt; True/False<br />\n<br />\n如<br />\n<br />\n英國法律統一，要所有電訊商用4G 做推廣，所以所有台都4G<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如美國<br />\nLTE 係反而快啲<br />\n<br />\n因為AT&amp;T iPhone 4S 就已經 show 4G (14.4mbps)<br />\n可以話係搞爛咗"},{"pid":"8cebad749a6d14d548ffb567aa33a390b2797266","tid":535983,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dis